HEADWORD: flavorless
<hw>fla"vor*less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without flavor;
tasteless. Opposite of <ant>flavorful</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bland, flat, flavourless, insipid,
savorless.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

